<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-851c0175-f55d-4dd8-bb0b-89e2c20c8d19'>
            
<p class="">4.12 p.m.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948">
                Mr. Brendan Bracken  (Bournemouth, East and Christchurch)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-01/debates/f970a3b4-4aa6-45ef-bc3b-2d06dc8ed4d1/CoalShortage#contribution-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I beg to move, to leave out from "that" to the end of the Question, and to add instead thereof: <blockquote><q>"this House deplores the contrast between Ministerial promises of adequate supplies and stocks of coal and the present shortages, which have inflicted great hardships in the home and threaten widespread industrial dislocation and stoppages."</q></blockquote></p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-01/debates/f970a3b4-4aa6-45ef-bc3b-2d06dc8ed4d1/CoalShortage#contribution-9ad81e43-91c3-4460-8415-66c112ea3948">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555">
                Mrs. Braddock  (Liverpool, Exchange)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-01/debates/f970a3b4-4aa6-45ef-bc3b-2d06dc8ed4d1/CoalShortage#contribution-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">On a point of order, Mr. Speaker. I wonder if I should be in order in asking you if you would please convey to the right hon. Member for Bournemouth, East and Christchurch (Mr. Bracken) before he speaks that any reference he makes to absenteeism by miners will be taken as very bad taste by this side of the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-01/debates/f970a3b4-4aa6-45ef-bc3b-2d06dc8ed4d1/CoalShortage#contribution-2411af53-2891-4e59-8301-dc7c57ec9555">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-60aa60af-5ccb-4afa-b9b6-bed2d4356640">
