        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-78c7899e-e288-476f-a173-f0c6a93af363">
                Lieut.-Commander Gurney Braith-waite (Bristol, North-West)
