                Mr. Bracken
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-345a4b2b-3c25-4954-9ac3-3dd135a09191" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
