                Mr. Glanville
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-39e06b0a-5b91-417c-8766-355e91916e1d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-02-01/debates/f970a3b4-4aa6-45ef-bc3b-2d06dc8ed4d1/CoalShortage#contribution-39e06b0a-5b91-417c-8766-355e91916e1d">
