<p class="">Is this in answer to my question, may I ask?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-21ae4167-239d-4a87-bbc7-23fbb9b2c618" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
